    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "indent": "prose",
      "color_name": "black",
      "spans": [
        {
          "text": "《红楼梦》旨义 是书题名极[多，一曰《红楼]",
          "size": 12.0,
          "font": "ËÎÌå",
          "color": 0,
          "color_name": "black",
          "page": 9,
          "page_height": 729.0,
          "bbox": [
            73.7,
            191.5,
            349.0,
            203.5
          ],
          "origin": [
            73.7,
            201.8
          ],
          "class": "body",
          "_line_id": 10,
          "_block_start": true
        },
        {
          "text": "②",
          "size": 10.0,
          "font": "ËÎÌå",
          "color": 0,
          "color_name": "black",
          "page": 9,
          "page_height": 729.0,
          "bbox": [
            349.0,
            193.3,
            358.9,
            203.2
          ],
          "origin": [
            349.0,
            201.8
          ],
          "class": "body",
          "_line_id": 10
        },
        {
          "text": "梦》，是总其全",
          "size": 12.0,
          "font": "ËÎÌå",
          "color": 0,
          "color_name": "black",
          "page": 9,
          "page_height": 729.0,
          "bbox": [
            359.0,
            191.5,
            442.3,
            203.5
          ],
          "origin": [
            359.0,
            201.8
          ],
          "class": "body",
          "_line_id": 10
        },
        {
          "text": "部之名也；又曰《风月宝鉴》，是戒妄动风月之情；又曰《石头记》，",
          "size": 12.0,
          "font": "ËÎÌå",
          "color": 0,
          "color_name": "black",
          "page": 9,
          "page_height": 729.0,
          "bbox": [
            73.7,
            213.5,
            447.1,
            225.5
          ],
          "origin": [
            73.7,
            223.8
          ],
          "class": "body",
          "_line_id": 11
        },
        {
          "text": "是自譬石头所记之事也。此三名皆书中曾已点睛矣。如宝玉作梦，梦中",
          "size": 12.0,
          "font": "ËÎÌå",
          "color": 0,
          "color_name": "black",
          "page": 9,
          "page_height": 729.0,
          "bbox": [
            73.7,
            235.6,
            442.2,
            247.6
          ],
          "origin": [
            73.7,
            245.9
          ],
          "class": "body",
          "_line_id": 12
        },
        {
          "text": "有曲，名曰《红楼梦十二支》，此则《红楼梦》之点睛。又如贾瑞病，",
          "size": 12.0,
          "font": "ËÎÌå",
          "color": 0,
          "color_name": "black",
          "page": 9,
          "page_height": 729.0,
          "bbox": [
            73.7,
            257.5,
            447.1,
            269.5
          ],
          "origin": [
            73.7,
            267.8
          ],
          "class": "body",
          "_line_id": 13
        },
        {
          "text": "跛道人持一镜来，上面即錾“风月宝鉴”四字，此则《风月宝鉴》之点",
          "size": 12.0,
          "font": "ËÎÌå",
          "color": 0,
          "color_name": "black",
          "page": 9,
          "page_height": 729.0,
          "bbox": [
            73.7,
            279.5,
            442.2,
            291.5
          ],
          "origin": [
            73.7,
            289.8
          ],
          "class": "body",
          "_line_id": 14
        },
        {
          "text": "睛。又如道人亲眼见石上大书一篇故事，则系石头所记之往来，此则《石",
          "size": 12.0,
          "font": "ËÎÌå",
          "color": 0,
          "color_name": "black",
          "page": 9,
          "page_height": 729.0,
          "bbox": [
            73.7,
            301.6,
            442.3,
            313.6
          ],
          "origin": [
            73.7,
            311.9
          ],
          "class": "body",
          "_line_id": 15
        },
        {
          "text": "头记》之点睛处。然此书又名曰《金陵十二钗》，审其名，则必系金陵",
          "size": 12.0,
          "font": "ËÎÌå",
          "color": 0,
          "color_name": "black",
          "page": 9,
          "page_height": 729.0,
          "bbox": [
            73.7,
            323.5,
            442.2,
            335.5
          ],
          "origin": [
            73.7,
            333.8
          ],
          "class": "body",
          "_line_id": 16
        },
        {
          "text": "十二女子也；然通部细搜检去，上中下女子岂止十二人哉！若云其中自",
          "size": 12.0,
          "font": "ËÎÌå",
          "color": 0,
          "color_name": "black",
          "page": 9,
          "page_height": 729.0,
          "bbox": [
            73.7,
            345.5,
            442.1,
            357.5
          ],
          "origin": [
            73.7,
            355.8
          ],
          "class": "body",
          "_line_id": 17
        },
        {
          "text": "有十二个，则又未尝指明白系某某，及至“红楼梦”一回中，亦曾翻出",
          "size": 12.0,
          "font": "ËÎÌå",
          "color": 0,
          "color_name": "black",
          "page": 9,
          "page_height": 729.0,
          "bbox": [
            73.7,
            367.6,
            442.1,
            379.6
          ],
          "origin": [
            73.7,
            377.9
          ],
          "class": "body",
          "_line_id": 18
        },
        {
          "text": "金陵十二钗之簿籍，又有十二支曲可考。 ",
          "size": 12.0,
          "font": "ËÎÌå",
          "color": 0,
          "color_name": "black",
          "page": 9,
          "page_height": 729.0,
          "bbox": [
            73.7,
            389.5,
            296.6,
            401.5
          ],
          "origin": [
            73.7,
            399.8
          ],
          "class": "body",
          "_line_id": 19
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "indent": "prose",
      "color_name": "black",
      "spans": [
        {
          "text": "书中凡写长安，在文人笔墨之间，则从古之称；凡愚夫妇、儿女子",
          "size": 12.0,
          "font": "ËÎÌå",
          "color": 0,
          "color_name": "black",
          "page": 9,
          "page_height": 729.0,
          "bbox": [
            73.7,
            411.5,
            442.3,
            423.5
          ],
          "origin": [
            73.7,
            421.8
          ],
          "class": "body",
          "_line_id": 20,
          "_block_start": true
        },
        {
          "text": "家常口角，则曰“中京”，是不欲着迹于方向也。盖天子之邦，亦当以",
          "size": 12.0,
          "font": "ËÎÌå",
          "color": 0,
          "color_name": "black",
          "page": 9,
          "page_height": 729.0,
          "bbox": [
            73.7,
            433.6,
            442.3,
            445.6
          ],
          "origin": [
            73.7,
            443.9
          ],
          "class": "body",
          "_line_id": 21
        },
        {
          "text": "中为尊，特避其东南西北四字样也。 ",
          "size": 12.0,
          "font": "ËÎÌå",
          "color": 0,
          "color_name": "black",
          "page": 9,
          "page_height": 729.0,
          "bbox": [
            73.7,
            455.5,
            272.5,
            467.5
          ],
          "origin": [
            73.7,
            465.8
          ],
          "class": "body",
          "_line_id": 22
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "indent": "prose",
      "color_name": "black",
      "spans": [
        {
          "text": "此书只是着意于闺中，故叙闺中之事切，略涉于外事者则简，不得",
          "size": 12.0,
          "font": "ËÎÌå",
          "color": 0,
          "color_name": "black",
          "page": 9,
          "page_height": 729.0,
          "bbox": [
            73.7,
            477.5,
            442.2,
            489.5
          ],
          "origin": [
            73.7,
            487.8
          ],
          "class": "body",
          "_line_id": 23,
          "_block_start": true
        },
        {
          "text": "谓其不均也。 ",
          "size": 12.0,
          "font": "ËÎÌå",
          "color": 0,
          "color_name": "black",
          "page": 9,
          "page_height": 729.0,
          "bbox": [
            73.7,
            499.6,
            152.0,
            511.6
          ],
          "origin": [
            73.7,
            509.9
          ],
          "class": "body",
          "_line_id": 24
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "indent": "prose",
      "color_name": "black",
      "spans": [
        {
          "text": "此书不敢干涉朝廷，凡有不得不用朝政者，只略用一笔带出，盖实",
          "size": 12.0,
          "font": "ËÎÌå",
          "color": 0,
          "color_name": "black",
          "page": 9,
          "page_height": 729.0,
          "bbox": [
            73.7,
            521.5,
            442.2,
            533.5
          ],
          "origin": [
            73.7,
            531.8
          ],
          "class": "body",
          "_line_id": 25,
          "_block_start": true
        },
        {
          "text": "不敢以写儿女之笔墨唐突朝廷之上也，又不得谓其不备。 ",
          "size": 12.0,
          "font": "ËÎÌå",
          "color": 0,
          "color_name": "black",
          "page": 9,
          "page_height": 729.0,
          "bbox": [
            73.7,
            543.5,
            381.0,
            555.5
          ],
          "origin": [
            73.7,
            553.8
          ],
          "class": "body",
          "_line_id": 26
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "indent": "prose",
      "color_name": "black",
      "spans": [
        {
          "text": "此书开卷第一回也，作者自云：因曾历过一番梦幻之后，故将真事",
          "size": 12.0,
          "font": "ËÎÌå",
          "color": 0,
          "color_name": "black",
          "page": 9,
          "page_height": 729.0,
          "bbox": [
            73.7,
            565.6,
            442.2,
            577.6
          ],
          "origin": [
            73.7,
            575.9
          ],
          "class": "body",
          "_line_id": 27,
          "_block_start": true
        },
        {
          "text": "隐去，而撰此《石头记》一书也。故曰“甄士隐梦幻识通灵”。但书中",
          "size": 12.0,
          "font": "ËÎÌå",
          "color": 0,
          "color_name": "black",
          "page": 9,
          "page_height": 729.0,
          "bbox": [
            73.7,
            587.5,
            442.3,
            599.5
          ],
          "origin": [
            73.7,
            597.8
          ],
          "class": "body",
          "_line_id": 28
        },
        {
          "text": "所记何事？又因何而撰是书哉？自云：今风尘碌碌，一事无成，忽念及",
          "size": 12.0,
          "font": "ËÎÌå",
          "color": 0,
          "color_name": "black",
          "page": 9,
          "page_height": 729.0,
          "bbox": [
            73.7,
            609.5,
            442.2,
            621.5
          ],
          "origin": [
            73.7,
            619.8
          ],
          "class": "body",
          "_line_id": 29
        },
        {
          "text": "当日所有之女子，一一细推了去，觉其行止见识皆出于我之上，何堂堂",
          "size": 12.0,
          "font": "ËÎÌå",
          "color": 0,
          "color_name": "black",
          "page": 9,
          "page_height": 729.0,
          "bbox": [
            73.7,
            631.6,
            442.1,
            643.6
          ],
          "origin": [
            73.7,
            641.9
          ],
          "class": "body",
          "_line_id": 30
        },
        {
          "text": "之须眉诚不若彼一干裙钗？实愧则有馀，悔则无益之大无可奈何之日",
          "size": 12.0,
          "font": "ËÎÌå",
          "color": 0,
          "color_name": "black",
          "page": 9,
          "page_height": 729.0,
          "bbox": [
            73.7,
            653.5,
            442.2,
            665.5
          ],
          "origin": [
            73.7,
            663.8
          ],
          "class": "body",
          "_line_id": 31
        },
        {
          "text": "也。当此时，则自欲将已往所赖——上赖天恩，下承祖德，锦衣纨袴之",
          "size": 12.0,
          "font": "ËÎÌå",
          "color": 0,
          "color_name": "black",
          "page": 10,
          "page_height": 729.0,
          "bbox": [
            73.7,
            80.2,
            442.3,
            92.2
          ],
          "origin": [
            73.7,
            90.5
          ],
          "class": "body",
          "_line_id": 35
        },
        {
          "text": "时，饫甘餍美之日，背父母教育之恩，负师兄规训之德，以致今日一事",
          "size": 12.0,
          "font": "ËÎÌå",
          "color": 0,
          "color_name": "black",
          "page": 10,
          "page_height": 729.0,
          "bbox": [
            73.7,
            102.1,
            442.3,
            114.1
          ],
          "origin": [
            73.7,
            112.4
          ],
          "class": "body",
          "_line_id": 36
        },
        {
          "text": "无成、半生潦倒之罪，编述一记，以告普天下人。虽我之罪固不能免，",
          "size": 12.0,
          "font": "ËÎÌå",
          "color": 0,
          "color_name": "black",
          "page": 10,
          "page_height": 729.0,
          "bbox": [
            73.7,
            124.2,
            447.1,
            136.2
          ],
          "origin": [
            73.7,
            134.5
          ],
          "class": "body",
          "_line_id": 37
        },
        {
          "text": "然闺阁中本自历历有人，万不可因我不肖，则一并使其泯灭也。虽今日",
          "size": 12.0,
          "font": "ËÎÌå",
          "color": 0,
          "color_name": "black",
          "page": 10,
          "page_height": 729.0,
          "bbox": [
            73.7,
            146.2,
            442.2,
            158.2
          ],
          "origin": [
            73.7,
            156.5
          ],
          "class": "body",
          "_line_id": 38
        },
        {
          "text": "之茅椽蓬牖，瓦灶绳床，其风晨月夕，阶柳庭花，亦未有伤于我之襟怀",
          "size": 12.0,
          "font": "ËÎÌå",
          "color": 0,
          "color_name": "black",
          "page": 10,
          "page_height": 729.0,
          "bbox": [
            73.7,
            168.1,
            442.3,
            180.1
          ],
          "origin": [
            73.7,
            178.4
          ],
          "class": "body",
          "_line_id": 39
        },
        {
          "text": "笔墨者。何为不用假语村言敷演出一段故事来，以悦人之耳目哉？故曰",
          "size": 12.0,
          "font": "ËÎÌå",
          "color": 0,
          "color_name": "black",
          "page": 10,
          "page_height": 729.0,
          "bbox": [
            73.7,
            190.2,
            442.3,
            202.2
          ],
          "origin": [
            73.7,
            200.5
          ],
          "class": "body",
          "_line_id": 40
        },
        {
          "text": "“[贾雨村]风尘怀闺秀”，乃是第一回题纲正义也。开卷即云“风尘怀",
          "size": 12.0,
          "font": "ËÎÌå",
          "color": 0,
          "color_name": "black",
          "page": 10,
          "page_height": 729.0,
          "bbox": [
            73.7,
            212.2,
            442.1,
            224.2
          ],
          "origin": [
            73.7,
            222.5
          ],
          "class": "body",
          "_line_id": 41
        },
        {
          "text": "闺秀”，则知作者本意原为记述当日闺友闺情，并非怨世骂时之书矣。",
          "size": 12.0,
          "font": "ËÎÌå",
          "color": 0,
          "color_name": "black",
          "page": 10,
          "page_height": 729.0,
          "bbox": [
            73.7,
            234.1,
            447.1,
            246.1
          ],
          "origin": [
            73.7,
            244.4
          ],
          "class": "body",
          "_line_id": 42
        },
        {
          "text": "虽一时有涉于世态，然亦不得不叙者，但非其本旨耳。阅者切记之。 ",
          "size": 12.0,
          "font": "ËÎÌå",
          "color": 0,
          "color_name": "black",
          "page": 10,
          "page_height": 729.0,
          "bbox": [
            73.7,
            256.2,
            441.1,
            268.2
          ],
          "origin": [
            73.7,
            266.5
          ],
          "class": "body",
          "_line_id": 43
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "indent": "prose",
      "color_name": "black",
      "spans": [
        {
          "text": "诗曰： ",
          "size": 12.0,
          "font": "ËÎÌå",
          "color": 0,
          "color_name": "black",
          "page": 10,
          "page_height": 729.0,
          "bbox": [
            73.7,
            278.2,
            140.0,
            290.2
          ],
          "origin": [
            73.7,
            288.5
          ],
          "class": "body",
          "_line_id": 44,
          "_block_start": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "poetry",
      "indent": true,
      "lines": [
        [
          {
            "text": "浮生着甚苦奔忙，盛席华筵终散场。 ",
            "size": 12.0,
            "font": "ËÎÌå",
            "color": 0,
            "color_name": "black",
            "page": 10,
            "page_height": 729.0,
            "bbox": [
              73.7,
              300.1,
              320.6,
              312.1
            ],
            "origin": [
              73.7,
              310.4
            ],
            "class": "poetry",
            "_line_id": 45,
            "_block_start": true
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "text": "悲喜千般同幻渺，古今一梦尽荒唐。 ",
            "size": 12.0,
            "font": "ËÎÌå",
            "color": 0,
            "color_name": "black",
            "page": 10,
            "page_height": 729.0,
            "bbox": [
              73.7,
              322.2,
              320.6,
              334.2
            ],
            "origin": [
              73.7,
              332.5
            ],
            "class": "poetry",
            "_line_id": 46,
            "_block_start": true
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "text": "谩言红袖啼痕重，更有情痴抱恨长。 ",
            "size": 12.0,
